00:02:18.120 --> 00:02:21.459
which consoles you currently are running on
and certainly doesn't give you any kind of

00:02:21.459 --> 00:02:23.819
warning that oh, this other account has been logged in?

00:02:23.819 --> 00:02:27.450
Or this same account has been logged in
on a new device.

00:02:27.450 --> 00:02:31.239
